text: Clarence Adrian "Clancy" Holland (born June 21, 1929) is an American politician who served in the Virginia Senate from the 7th district from 1984 to 1996. He spent fifty-three years working as a family physician. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1929 births Category:Living people Category:Virginia state senators Category:Mayors of Virginia Beach, Virginia Category:Virginia Democrats Category:Physicians from Virginia
